headline: DAT: Truckload volumes, spot rates dipped in August
summary: BEAVERTON, Ore., September 19, 2025--Demand for truckload services cooled in August after July’s tariff-driven pull-forward of imports, according to DAT Freight & Analytics, which operates the DAT One freight marketplace and DAT iQ data analytics service.
